document_data.Abilities:
Air myrmidons were immune to the effects of [[disease]]s and [[poison]]s, as they were composed wholly of elemental essence.{{Cite dragon/361/Ecology of the Fire Archon|43}} 

They had some resistance to lightning-based [[spell]]s or abilities, as well as ones that were sonic-based. They also had innate abilities allowing them to temporarily imbue their weapons with electrical energy and speed around the battlefield.

Zephyrhaunts could transform themselves into raging cyclones, flinging away the enemies they moved through, while tempestblades could encase themselves in an aura of screaming winds that turned aside all weaponry lunged at them.
